/>\n一開始啲女權有位入就係因為好多人都啞忍<br />\n<br />\n支持啲人企出黎<br />\n但定罪前唔好攻擊被告（喺啲無法治嘅地方另計）<br />\n同埋唔好講咩無罪唔等於無做呢啲弱智嘅人格謀殺<br />\n社會先會有公義"},{"pid":"8981f818ba305309352fc5d1650011d04af7f72f","tid":1149413,"uid":125760,"like":31,"dislike":6,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T10:11:54.000Z","msg":"下，係carousell 傾好哂，銀行入數收唔到貨，報警都拉佢唔入咩？ 有哂對話紀錄，入數紀錄wo"},{"pid":"ebb7c44b968e1ae6e7be21ce5e43cc9995e36dfe","tid":1149413,"uid":235152,"like":66,"dislike":4,"score":62,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T10:18:56.000Z","msg":"14歲自己識組隊捉賊勁到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我14歲果時都只係識入隊同人講女同學身材同邊個露底<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1bcc9b6af6f6df43878085a0ba330961eb24fd7","tid":1149413,"uid":179967,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T10:20:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下，係carousell 傾好哂，銀行入數收唔到貨，報警都拉佢唔入咩？ 有哂對話紀錄，入數紀錄wo</blockquote><br />\n警察唔受喎<br />\n我有時都懷疑以前俾人呃點數話搵得番條友留案底都係鳩嗡"},{"pid":"a6a19b7ddbe3914f76b0cee7703620d3bc54e13a","tid":1149413,"uid":178800,"like":3,"dislike":63,"score":-60,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T10:21:31.000Z","msg":"14歲女熟哂<br />\n<br />\n西已臭"},{"pid":"d5a6ab74fbf31b8f9fab005ff36a2728a9950904","tid":1149413,"uid":38904,"like":42,"dislike":3,"score":39,"quote":{"pid":"a6a19b7ddbe3914f76b0cee7703620d3bc54e13a","tid":1149413,"uid":178800,"like":3,"dislike":63,"score":-60,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T10:21:31.000Z","msg":"14歲女熟哂<br />\n<br />\n西已臭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T10:22:50.000Z","msg":"邊夠你老母臭"},{"pid":"3973e7fff090a6ec9797c575db3c13fa053d9ccc","tid":1149413,"uid":165336,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T10:25:00.000Z","msg":"香港警賊垃圾到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要個細路女搞咁撚多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi